{
  "stem": "26731.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Hadn't been the murder of the, uh, secretary in Paris or the embassy secretary, but something else would happen [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Definitely, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The population, the people, who didn't do it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, they were quite taken aback.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Definitely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was a group that-- uh-- oh, some gangs were actually-- that was correct.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course didn't talk to them, but, uh, I only can tell what the non-Jewish relatives, of course, they were appalled.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some people, for no other reason, this was again, order is very important in Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How could it happen?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People go around breaking windows and, um, lay fire to synagogues.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, that's unheard of.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was not very helpful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "See, I think they didn't realize what would happen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Kristallnacht did not have the expected effect.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Wasn't aware of what happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] for instance, there was some-- one synagogue was located, uh, close to apartment buildings.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They came and wanted to burn it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a policeman standing there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Are you out of your mind?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If you do this, you will cause [INAUDIBLE] flames.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I would say, people were not standing there and laughing and applauding, not at all.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Maybe in some cases.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I understand, however, much worse outside Berlin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Much worse.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In Berlin, too, it was a big city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Many, uh, people of foreign countries, diplomats, I guess, realized that, uh-- however, what they did, arrested many Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Many of my teachers that was in the Jewish high school, uh, were taken in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I remember I took home a little letter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because of special circumstances, the report cards will be late this year.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Everybody knew what the special circumstances were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This I remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And even some distant relative was arrested too and [INAUDIBLE] Sachsenhausen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, definitely.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
